<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/21726388">《出师表》写的那样倾尽全力，感人至深。刘禅看了以后有什么反应？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="871519" data-action="/question/detail">

